{"word":"G4824 - συμβούλιον - symboúlion - soom-boo'-lee-on - Consultation","sections":[{"paragraph":"<strong>மூல வார்த்தை / Original: </strong><span class=\"hebrewOrGreek\">συμβούλιον</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>எழுத்துமாற்றம் / Transliteration: </strong><span class=\"transliteration\">symboúlion</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>ஒலிபெயர்ப்பு / Phonetic: </strong><span class=\"phonetic\">soom-boo'-lee-on</span>"},{"paragraph":"<strong>சுருக்க விளக்கம் / Short Definition: </strong><span class=\"short-definition\">Consultation</span>"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"parts-of-speech\"><strong>இலக்கண சொல்வகை / Part(s) of speech: </strong>Noun Neuter / பெயர்ச்சொல் (அஃறிணை)</span>"},{"paragraph":"ஆலோசனை, யோசனை - பால் வேறுபாடற்ற பெயர்ச்சொல்"},{"paragraph":"1. counsel"},{"paragraph":"2. a council, an assembly of counsellors or persons in consultation"},{"paragraph":"<span class=\"original-in-english\"><strong>ஆங்கில மூலம் / Original in English: </strong>Neuter of a presumed derivative of <a href=\"#/G4825 - σύμβουλος - sýmboulos - soom'-boo-los/4825\">G4825</a>; <i>advisement</i>; specifically a <i>deliberative</i> body, that is, the provincial <i>assessors</i> or lay court: - consultation, counsel, council.</span>"},{"paragraph":""}]}